These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
House: ranch-style, modern, townhouse, cottage
Job: journalist, mechanic, project-manager, entrepreneur
1. Job:mechanic is on the left of Job:journalist##1
2. House:ranch-style == Job:entrepreneur##1
3. Job:project-manager is on the right of Job:journalist##1
4. House:modern is on the left of Job:entrepreneur##1
5. House:cottage is on the left of Job:journalist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| House          | cottage | townhouse | modern | ranch-style   |
| Job   | mechanic  | journalist     | project-manager   | entrepreneur |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Cigar: chaman, oliveros, tiparillo, alhambra
Beverage: soy-milk, mirinda, fanta, water
1. Cigar:alhambra == Beverage:mirinda##1
2. Cigar:chaman is on the far right##1
3. Cigar:oliveros is on the right of Cigar:alhambra##1
4. Cigar:alhambra is on the right of Beverage:fanta##1
5. Beverage:mirinda is on the left of Beverage:soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar   | tiparillo | alhambra | oliveros | chaman    |
| Beverage   | fanta    | mirinda      | soy-milk | water |

