2. Color:yellow == Transport:motorbike##1
3. Transport:scooter is on the far right##1
4. Transport:tram is on the right of Color:mauve##1
5. Color:white is on the left of Transport:scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Color         | yellow | mauve | white   | blue |
| Transport   | motorbike   | bus | tram | scooter         |

